ZH: 这片地区以高大的树木而闻名。
EN: This area is well known for its tall trees.

ZH: 这座公园里栽种了许多不同类型的树木。
EN: Many different types of trees are planted in this park.

ZH: 树木给我们提供了新鲜的空气和氧气。
EN: Trees provide us with fresh air and oxygen.

ZH: 在这个季节，树木上的叶子都变成了红色。
EN: During this season, the leaves on the trees have turned red.

ZH: 稀疏的树木使得这个地方看起来更加荒凉。
EN: The sparse trees make this place look even more desolate.

ZH: 这片森林里的树木年龄都非常古老。
EN: The trees in this forest are all very old.

ZH: 树木的根部十分坚固，能够扎根在土地里。
EN: The roots of the trees are very strong and can anchor into the ground.

ZH: 树木的枝条在风中轻轻摇曳。
EN: The branches of the trees sway gently in the wind.

ZH: 这片区域的树木被铺上了一层薄雪。
EN: The trees in this area are covered with a thin layer of snow.

ZH: 树木和花草共同构成了这座花园的美丽景色。
EN: The trees and flowers together create the beautiful scenery of this garden.

ZH: 树木是大自然的珍贵财富。
EN: Trees are a precious treasure of nature.

ZH: 始终保护树木是我们的责任。
EN: It is our responsibility to always protect trees.

ZH: 孩子们在树木下追逐着彼此。
EN: The children are chasing each other under the trees.

ZH: 一阵大风折断了这棵树木的枝条。
EN: A strong gust of wind broke the branches of this tree.

ZH: 树木的阴影为我们提供了避暑的凉爽地方。
EN: The shade of the trees provides us with a cool place to escape from the heat.

ZH: 我们需要种植更多的树木来改善环境。
EN: We need to plant more trees to improve the environment.

ZH: 需要几十年的时间才能让一棵树木生长得如此高大。
EN: It takes several decades for a tree to grow so tall.

ZH: 这些树木帮助保护了河流的水源。
EN: These trees help protect the water source of the river.

ZH: 这片树木茂密的森林是野生动物的栖息地。
EN: This densely wooded forest is the habitat for many wild animals.

ZH: 这片土地上原本生长着茂盛的树木，但现在已经被砍伐一空。
EN: This land used to be covered with lush trees, but now it has been cleared.
